## Specs-D2 RelationsPanel & AutoLinkContent
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/components/`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-A1

```typescript
// RelationsPanel.vue
interface RelationsPanelProps {
  item: SpecItem
}

// AutoLinkContent.vue
interface AutoLinkContentProps {
  content: string
}
// Regex: /\b([GRAPTVXIS]\d+(?:\.\d+)?)\b/
```

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `parents` | `{ id, title, section_type, status }[]` | Upstream depends_on |
| `children` | `{ id, title, section_type, status }[]` | Downstream related |

```
fn render(content):
    parts = splitByRegex(content, ID_REF_REGEX)
    for part in parts:
        if part.matches(ID_REF_REGEX):
            render(<SpecLink id={part} />)
        else:
            render(<span>{part}</span>)
```


