## Specs-D3 GateBanner (Specs View)
**Status:** implemented
**Module:** `packages/auto-forge-ui/src/components/GateBanner.vue`
**Tags:** stack:frontend
**Depends on:** UiSystem-A1, Relay-D6

```typescript
interface GateBannerProps {
  sectionId: string
  gate: PendingGate
}

// Events
emit('approve', gateId: string)
emit('reject', gateId: string)
emit('openInChat', gateId: string)
```

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Hidden: no active gate for section
    Hidden --> Visible: gate_reached for this section
    Visible --> Hidden: gate_resolved or approved
    Visible --> Expanded: user clicks View Diff
    Expanded --> Visible: user collapses diff
```

| Field | Type | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `sectionId` | `string` | Which spec section this banner guards |
| `gate.profession` | `string` | Who is waiting (e.g., "architect") |
| `gate.title` | `string` | One-line summary of what needs approval |
| `gate.since` | `number` | Timestamp when gate was reached |


